channel.title: Looking for help
channel.description:
Hey guys, I'm obviously new, But I'm looking for help on starting my first Rsps. I know some of the basics, I just really want someone to help me construct a Rsps. I'm looking to create anything in the 667-723 range. I'm willing to learn, I just need a good teacher. If someone can get back to me I'd appreciate it. If anyone could leave their skype name if you're willing to help I will add you and we'll get started :).
Thanks for your time.
Please keep in mind I will always give you credits.
